05_API/sidebar.html.body:
侧边栏
服务：$sidebar
示例：

  .device-ios { width: 467px; height: 800px; background: url(../img/devices-sprite.jpg) center top no-repeat; background-size: 467px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
  .demo-ios { margin-top: 85px; width: 320px; height: 568px; }






用法：





          Show Sidebar







  export default {
    data() {
      return {
        menuButtonText: '',
        sidebar: undefined,
        sidebarRight: undefined
      }
    },

    mounted() {
      let template = `

        No man is an island,
        entire of itself.
        Every man is a piece of the continent,
        a part of the main.
        If a clod be washed away by the sea,
        Europe is the less,
        as well as if a promontory were,
        as well as if a manor of thy friend's or of thine own were.
        Any man's death diminishes me.
        Because I am involved in mankind.
        And,
        therefore,
        never send to know for whom the bells tolls,
        it tolls for thee.

      `
      this.sidebar = $sidebar.fromTemplate(template, {position: 'left'})

      this.sidebarRight = $sidebar.fromTemplate('右边栏', {position: 'right'})
    },

    destroyed() {
      // 注销所有 Sidebar 实例
      $sidebar.destroy()
    },

    methods: {
      toggleSidebar() {
        this.sidebar.toggle()
      },

      toggleSidebarRight() {
        this.sidebarRight.toggle()
      }
    }
  }


方法：
Sidebar fromTemplate(template: String, options: Object)

按模板字符串创建侧边栏实例

Sidebar fromTemplateUrl(templateUrl: String, options: Object)

按远程模板地址返回的模板字符串创建侧边栏实例

Sidebar 实例方法：
Void toggle()
切换
Void open()
打开
Void close()
